{"tid":1728261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"量子速讀","createTime":"2019-11-16T19:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:48:58.000Z","uid":240409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a42c5f0c160260eba6e1169172b95b652958845","tid":1728261,"uid":240409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T19:48:14.000Z","msg":"量子速讀已經過時， 依家係蒸氣吸收法.<br />\n<br />\n首先將沖完涼嘅水(因為嗰啲係你嘅精華)，浸透本書<br />\n<br />\n 然後將已浸透嘅書， 放喺太陽曬乾， 咁就完成， 你就可以背到成本書。<br />\n<br />\n呢種方法嘅好處 <br />\n▶️ 你想幾多本書都可以<br />\n<br />\n呢種方法既原理<br />\n▶️ 將你啲精華浸透咗落本書度， 將佢蒸發， 你嘅精華係標記， 透過太陽嘅光線帶返落你到， 咁你就可以背到成本書"},{"pid":"f0cf73727c600a1ef02e548103101de9503929e8","tid":1728261,"uid":81942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T19:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}